<h3>Muscat Maintainance Report for <%=@base_model%></h3>
<strong>Note</strong> the includes all authority files that had at least one souce with non-matching values, and it triggers a resave of all the sources of the authority.
        <p>
            <h4>Authority files that triggered resave:</h4>
            <% @models.each do |model, errors|%>
            <p><b><%=model%></b><br>
                <% errors.each do |message, ids|%>
                Error message: <i><%=message%></i><br>
                <%=@base_model%> IDs: <%=ids.join(", ")%><br>
                <%end%>
            <%end%>
            </p>
            <b>Saved <%=@base_model.to_s.pluralize%>: </b><%=@saved_source_count%><br>
            <% if @unsavable_sources.count > 0 %>
            <b>Could not save these <%=@base_model.to_s.pluralize%>: <b><%=@unsavable_sources.join(" ")%><br>
                    <%end%>
        </p>
        <h6><%=@message%>